":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/31/dM/tI/s102/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–31, div. M, title I, § 102(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-05-05"},"text":"May 5, 2017","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/131/800"},"text":"131 Stat. 800","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb79577a3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb79577a4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idb79577a5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Part F, referred to in subsec. (a)(1)(B)(i), was classified to section 681 et seq. of this title, prior to repeal by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/193/tI/s108/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–193, title I, § 108(e)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-08-22"},"text":"Aug. 22, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/2167"},"text":"110 Stat. 2167","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s682"},"text":"Section 682 of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in subsec. (a)(2)(A), (B), was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/193/tI/s108/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–193, title I, § 108(e)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-08-22"},"text":"Aug. 22, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/2167"},"text":"110 Stat. 2167","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Indian Self-Determination and Education Assistance Act, referred to in subsecs. (b)(1)(F) and (e)(2), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/638"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–638","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-04"},"text":"Jan. 4, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/2203"},"text":"88 Stat. 2203","children":[],"tail":", which was classified principally to subchapter II (§ 450 et seq.) of chapter 14 of Title 25, Indians, prior to editorial reclassification as chapter 46 (§ 5301 et seq.) of Title 25. Section 5 of the Act was classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s450c"},"text":"section 450c of Title 25","children":[],"tail":" prior to editorial reclassification as "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s5305"},"text":"section 5305 of Title 25","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s5301"},"text":"section 5301 of Title 25","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idb79577a6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 612, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1935-08-14/ch531/tIV/s412"},"text":"act Aug. 14, 1935, ch. 531, title IV, § 412","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-06-17"},"text":"June 17, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/272/tIII/s303"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–272, title III, § 303","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/528"},"text":"94 Stat. 528","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/tXXIII/s2306/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35, title XXIII, § 2306(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/846"},"text":"95 Stat. 846","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248/tI/s155/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248, title I, § 155(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/397"},"text":"96 Stat. 397","children":[],"tail":", related to prorating shelter allowance for AFDC family living with another household, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/193/s103/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–193, § 103(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", as amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/33/tV/s5514/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–33, title V, § 5514(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-08-05"},"text":"Aug. 5, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/620"},"text":"111 Stat. 620","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idb79577a7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2017—Subsec. (a)(1)(A), (2)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/31"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–31","children":[],"tail":" substituted “each of fiscal years 2017 and 2018” for “fiscal year 2012”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2012—Subsec. (a)(1)(A), (2)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/96"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–96","children":[],"tail":" substituted “fiscal year 2012” for “each of fiscal years 1997, 1998, 1999, 2000, 2001, 2002, and 2003”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2003—Subsec. (a)(1)(A), (2)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/40"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–40","children":[],"tail":" substituted “2002, and 2003” for “and 2002”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2000—Subsec. (a)(3)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/554"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–554","children":[],"tail":" substituted “603(a)(5)(H)” for “603(a)(5)(I)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1999—Subsec. (a)(3)(C)(ii). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/113"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–113","children":[],"tail":" substituted “clause (viii)” for “clause (vii)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1997—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/33/s5514/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–33, § 5514(c)","children":[],"tail":", made technical amendment to directory language of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/193/s103/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–193, § 103(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", which enacted this section."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(1)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/33/s5508/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–33, § 5508(a)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “which shall be reduced for a fiscal year, on a pro rata basis for each quarter, in the case of a tribal family assistance plan approved during a fiscal year for which the plan is to be in effect,” before “and shall”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/33/s5508/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–33, § 5508(b)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “For each of fiscal years 1997, 1998, 1999, 2000, 2001, and 2002, the Secretary shall pay to each eligible Indian tribe that proposes to operate a program described in subparagraph (C)” for “The Secretary shall pay to each eligible Indian tribe for each of fiscal years 1997, 1998, 1999, 2000, 2001, and 2002”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2)(C).